snippet.title: DatePixel 2.0 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Official Trailer for DatePixel 2.0!
Coming Wednesday, 8/12!

Date your favorite character from NoPixel, the Twitch based GTA Roleplay server! With 8 main routes to chose from, there are hours of content to explore, and some secret endings to be found!

This project was made by Artist Gang Gang during a 48 hour game jam, and is a passionate fan project meant to celebrate a community that has given us a lot of joy! Please enjoy! 



Special thanks to Choi for the voice clip! https://twitch.tv/choi

––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––
DatePixel can be found here: https://artganggang.itch.io/datepixel
––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––
